---
title: Cauliflower & Chickpea Tikka Masala with Rice, Yogurt & Cilantro
description: If you’ve ever been daunted by the idea of making curry at home, you’re in luck! We’ll send you all the spices you need plus a sauce base that makes this vegetarian curry super easy and convenient to make. Cauliflower is roasted with curry powder then finishes cooking with chickpeas in the tikka masala sauce. Serve it all over a bed of jasmine rice, drizzle with yogurt, then sprinkle with cilantro leaves for a seriously good curry for when you’re in a hurry (or even if you’re not!).
